00:19:01,047 --> 00:19:02,147
Aku bisa duduk di kursi depan!

362
00:19:02,147 --> 00:19:04,647
Apa, lagi? Itu tidak adil!

363
00:19:04,647 --> 00:19:08,947
Genta! Kau harus biarkan kami duduk di kursi depan juga sesekali!

364
00:19:08,947 --> 00:19:13,347
Ayolah... Jangan bertengkar dan lekas masuk!

365
00:19:13,347 --> 00:19:14,847
Baik, batu-kertas-gunting!

366
00:19:14,847 --> 00:19:16,247
Conan, tolong kemari!

367
00:19:16,247 --> 00:19:17,247
Jangan pedulikan dia!

368
00:19:17,247 --> 00:19:19,247
Benar!

